not a discoverable behavior.

title: Add huge performance improvements
message:
Add huge performance improvements

- Address potential activity memory leaks, by allowing callers to unregister handlers, listeners or validators. Actually, MaoniActivity will auto-clear strong references when it exits. This requires callers to reset their handlers when they are done. Furthermore, Maoni#start(...) can no longer be called twice.

- Reduce memory footprint when loading image views (especially, screen captures). Thumbnail preview has been reduced to a 100x100 size, since it does not need to be loaded at full resolution.

title: Re-organize into different sub-modules and fix screenshot file sharing
message:
Re-organize into different sub-modules and fix screenshot file sharing

- maoni-common: Java Gradle projet, containing common classes and end-user contract (validator, handler, and listener interfaces)
 - maoni-email: Java Gradle project, containing a listener responsible for opening up an Intent for sending out emails with the feedback collected. Depends on maoni-common
 - maoni-maoni: actual Android Library project. Depends on maoni-common
 - maoni-sample: actual sample Android application. Depends on both maoni-maoni and maoni-email
